parameters:
Captain Clevo: Bring the luggage into the hideout. You
don't have to kill the nobles, but intimidate them enough so
they won't resist.

Emma, a member of the thief gang: C-Captain! It seems like
there was a woman inside the carriage!

Captain Clevo: I'll take them to the camp. Those nobles
were planning to use them as toys.

Emma, a member of the thief gang: T-That's different from
the usual--
Emma, a member of the thief gang: Captain!

Captain Clevo: ...So this is the rumored beast, stay away
from it, all of you.

Captain Clevo: I want to knock them out without causing any
injuries, but I don't want any broken bones.

Captain Clevo: I apologize for not being able to go easy on
you when you woke up.

Captain Clevo: Do you understand? Eat bread, food, anything
to fill your stomach for now.

Captain Clevo: Someone bring water and cloth. We can't have
them staying naked forever.

The day they attacked the henchmen of Pido, a noble of the
Senate who had taken their land. It was by chance that the
Emma thief gang encountered Nora and helped her. However,
this chance encounter would give birth to the thief Nora.

Nora had an intuitive feeling that Captain Clevo was not her
enemy. His attitude was completely different from the men
she had met before. While she was bewildered by his
kindness, it was also the first moment of relief for her.

From that moment on, bread became a special food for Nora.
It was the food given to her by the hero who rescued her,
and above all, its fluffy texture was incredibly delicious.

Due to Captain Clevo's judgment, Nora was to be hidden in
the hideout of the Emma Thief Gang. Captain Clevo absolutely
could not tolerate Nora being a target of the 'Beast Hunt'.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
